## Input
```bython
enum class Color:
    case Red, Green
    case Blue


enum class Expr:
    case Lit(value: int)
    case Add(left: int, right: int)

    def eval(self) -> int:
        match self:
            case Lit(v):
                return v
            case Add(a, b):
                return a + b
```

